# Demo: JD.AI Startup
# Shows provider detection and welcome banner

Output docs/images/demo-startup.gif

Set Shell "pwsh"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set Padding 20

Type "jdai"
Enter
Sleep 5s

# Show the welcome banner and provider detection
Screenshot docs/images/demo-startup.png
Sleep 2s
